comments: Crowder (MIL) brings his hand toward Booker's (PHX) space and marginal contact occurs as he receives the pass.
Crowder (MIL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Booker's (PHX) arm.
Okogie (PHX) applies a stayed hand to Ingles's (MIL) body that does not affect his dribble or SQBR.
Ingles (MIL) is already in Okogie's (PHX) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver.
Paul (PHX) brings his arm toward Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs during Holiday's drive.
Paul (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Holiday (MIL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Paul (PHX) brings his hand toward Middleton's (MIL) hip and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in Booker's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Booker (PHX) wraps his right arm around Holiday's (MIL) back while defending the drive, after the illegal contact he swipes down and dislodges the ball.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Holiday's (MIL) path and absorbs the incidental contact during the screen.
Booker (PHX) dislodges the ball away from Holiday (MIL) as the shot clock expires and a 24 second violation is correctly called.
Booker (PHX) dislodges the ball away from Holiday (MIL) as the shot clock expires. The possession is correctly awarded to the Suns.
Holiday (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position and incidental contact occurs as Holiday  defends in the post.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Lopez (MIL) establishes his left foot as his pivot, and he lifts it before releasing his dribble.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Booker (PHX) brushes Lopez's (MIL) arm and marginal contact occurs during Lopez's (MIL) shot attempt near the rim.
Holiday (MIL) brings his arm toward Booker's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs during Booker's  drive.
Booker (PHX) goes to, not through, Holiday's (MIL) space and marginal contact occurs as Booker releases away during the drive.
Holiday (MIL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Booker (PHX) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Ingles (MIL).
Replay review of the OOB called on MIL pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Ross (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.
Paul (PHX) and Lopez (MIL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Lee (PHX) initiates contact with Holiday's (MIL) arm and affects Holiday's ability to maintain the possession.
Ingles (MIL) moves in Booker's (PHX) space and affects his upward shooting motion.
Lee (PHX) makes marginal contact with Lopez's (MIL) arm as time expires.
